The world's first and only <strong>Hed Kandi Beach Bar</strong>, opened in March 2007 to incredible acclaim...<br><br>With award-winning decor, chic cuisine and tons of fabulous fun to be had, this is certainly a must for any clubber visiting <a href="/africa/egypt/hurghada">Hurghada</a>.<br><br>The weekly programme of  themes runs along the lines of the successful compilation albums from Serve Chilled, to Disco Kandi and Twisted Disco... <br><br>With two monthly-ish 'special events' Hed Kandi LIVE (usually on the second Saturday of the month) flies in a UK Hed Kandi resident and then Full Moon Party with  Hed Kandi Egypt residents - both events are accompanied by Craig Hume on LIVE saxophone!<br></div>
